Version 2.0beta1 - internally released 2013-11-05
cmb     adapted for CMSimple_XH 1.6
cmb     added possibility to suppress checkboxes by leaving pagedata_attribute empty and made that the default (suggested by Jerry)
cmb     replaced "cmsimple" theme with original themes
cmb     made system check implicit
cmb     removed out-dated language files
cmb     updated English and German manual, and removed others
cmb     improved performance (especially, for many pages)
cmb     added CSRF protection
cmb     removed dependency on Utf8_XH plugin
cmb     fixed invalid markup
cmb     refactored PHP code to MVC
cmb     refactored JS code to use namespace
cmb     added unit tests and developer documentation

Version 1pl15 - released 2013-10-29
cmb     fixed bug, where modified jstree.js relied on $ (reported by johnjdoe)
cmb     replaced plugin icon

Version 1pl14 - released 2013-10-11
cmb     fixed bug, where error message was suppressed when saving failed
cmb     fixed issue with regard to some templates (reported by Torsten.Behrens)
cmb     replaced deprecated preg_replace('//e') with preg_replace_callback()
cmb     improved tooltip of help icon
cmb     added phing build.xml

Version 1pl13 - released 2013-08-06
cmb     added creation of backup before saving the modified contents
cmb     removed dependency on deprecated jQuery functions
cmb     removed icons from dialog titles for compatibility with jQueryUI 1.10
cmb     improved redirection after saving

Version 1pl12 - released 2013-05-16
